    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure definition of ADC analog watchdog. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The setting of these parameters by function <ref refid="group__ADC__Exported__Functions__Group3_1ga7e992cf20f0fdc90cf558bc13dd6995c" kindref="member">HAL_ADC_AnalogWDGConfig()</ref> is conditioned to ADC state. ADC state can be either:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>For all parameters: ADC disabled or ADC enabled without conversion on going on ADC groups regular and injected. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
